        &kp CAPS  &kp A     &kp S    &kp D    &kp F      &kp G  &none    &hm LGUI SPACE &kp LALT &none &none &kp LGUI  &kp RCTRL            &none &kp H  &kp J  &kp K     &kp L    &kp SEMI &kp SQT
